The director of the company addresses the employees:
- The anniversary of our company is approaching and it needs to be celebrated so that the whole of Moscow speaks about it, at the same time to meet the minimum budget, and of course the anniversary should bring great joy to all employees. We are throwing ideas!
A voice from the crowd:
- You need to jump from the Ostankino Tower. The whole of Moscow will know about this, it will be inexpensive, and as for the joy of employees...
